{"tw": {"3670820": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Restore", "steam_appid": 3670820, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/33a6d50ae0e2b93539f18cdfbaec7f96.avif?t=1775808394\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >翔一、梓羽與艾米莉被召喚至異世界。就在他們即將與魔王對峙時，魔王卻逃入另一個世界。為了回到原本的世界，他們只得緊追而去。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不久後，他們發現自身的能力被神秘封印，變得如同普通人一般無能為力。國王卡爾迪爾垂涎梓羽的力量，於是她自願留下，以換取翔一與艾米莉的自由。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >察覺不對勁的梓羽，臨行前囑咐他們務必蒐集情報。翔一與艾米莉很快察覺，他們早已身陷一場危險的權力鬥爭之中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >距離談判結束只剩一週，他們必須在時間耗盡前查明真相，拯救梓羽。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/3e60e56bac2fe5e7f421b1e9c525c999.avif?t=1775808394\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作具備經典RPG玩法要素，包括戰鬥、學習新技能、角色強化與探索世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以拯救落入邪惡之手的夥伴——若已來不及，也能替他們討回公道。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/e09ecf40e11892301e6aa6295ccbbd0c.avif?t=1775808394\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/765678ced7c89a7782c2f08381a16ab2.avif?t=1775808394\" width=739 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/a3b06439d18a0d112e1b6b4a96cf5827.avif?t=1775808394\" width=739 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/82394e27829426f5768bcee135cdd639.avif?t=1775808394\" width=739 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/d9cbd3c0ebac7a4a54840e69e056382b.avif?t=1775808394\" width=739 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/7152c3c273ba63d33b97e90f6c51613d.avif?t=1775808394\" width=739 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/35072c7e2ff63808a82b81ff1b16228f.avif?t=1775808394\" width=739 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/bd6af3464b443a19ce6c11d2f49b1ecc.avif?t=1775808394\" width=739 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/71ea01366751d44086e41bd47babb8cd.avif?t=1775808394\" width=739 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/6da4973329603fb0089d68fb6375bb47.avif?t=177580