\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/e09ecf40e11892301e6aa6295ccbbd0c.avif?t=1775808394\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/765678ced7c89a7782c2f08381a16ab2.avif?t=1775808394\" width=739 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/a3b06439d18a0d112e1b6b4a96cf5827.avif?t=1775808394\" width=739 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/82394e27829426f5768bcee135cdd639.avif?t=1775808394\" width=739 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/d9cbd3c0ebac7a4a54840e69e056382b.avif?t=1775808394\" width=739 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/7152c3c273ba63d33b97e90f6c51613d.avif?t=1775808394\" width=739 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/35072c7e2ff63808a82b81ff1b16228f.avif?t=1775808394\" width=739 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/bd6af3464b443a19ce6c11d2f49b1ecc.avif?t=1775808394\" width=739 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/71ea01366751d44086e41bd47babb8cd.avif?t=1775808394\" width=739 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/6da4973329603fb0089d68fb6375bb47.avif?t=1775808394\" width=739 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/d22ed122c4e572d1bc8a18c728f207f6.avif?t=1775808394\" width=739 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/f91eb72d8da5ec5ddbf71ff87f814415.avif?t=1775808394\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>RPG體驗</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >擊敗敵人獲得經驗值並提升等級。學習新技能並嘗試各種技能搭配，靈活應對各種挑戰。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>資源管理</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >謹慎分配有限的資源（如時間與金錢），才能在旅途中穩紮穩打、走得更遠。</p>", "short_description": "在這款RPG中，你將扮演翔一，並與梓羽和艾米莉一同被召喚至異世界。你們的能力遭到了封印，僅能依靠智慧與夥伴合作生存。你能守護他們並平安返家嗎？", "supported_languages": "英文, 日文, 簡體中文, 繁體中文", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/83e45cba768510bd678f876c4b79f0e7d9fb2246/header.jpg?t=1775808394", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/09844b32cee94b7c6abce5564e89ad7a7753db3b/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1775808394", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/09844b32cee94b7c6abce5564e89ad7a7753db3b/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1775808394", "website": "https://saikeystudios.com", "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> Windows® 7/8/8.1/10<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Core2 Duo or better<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 4 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> DirectX 9/OpenGL 4.1 capable GPU<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 2 GB 可用空間</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [], "legal_notice": "2026 Saikey Studios", "developers": ["Momimomi Studio"], "publishers": ["Saikey Studios"], "price_overview": {"currency": "TWD", "initial": 17200, "final": 17200, "discount_percent": 0, "initial_formatted": "", "final_formatted": "NT$ 172"}, "categories": [{"id": 2, "description": "單人"}, {"id": 22, "description": "Steam 成就"}, {"id": 23, "description": "Steam 雲端"}, {"id": 62, "description": "親友同享"}], "genres": [{"id": "25", "description": "冒險"}, {"id": "3", "description": "角色扮演"}], "release_date": {"coming_soon": false, "date": "2026 年 3 月 27 日"}}}}, "us": {"3670820": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Restore", "steam_appid": 3670820, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/67adf54c2475c340daf42c5cf8d4b234.avif?t=1775808394\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shouichi, Azuha, and Emily are summoned to another world, but just as they confront the Demon Lord, she escapes to another realm. With no choice, they must follow her to return home. However, they soon discover their abilities are mysteriously sealed, leaving them as ordinary, powerless humans. Azuha, whose powers are desired by King Caldier, volunteers to stay behind in exchange for Shouichi and Emily’s freedom. Feeling something is off, Azuha urges them to gather intel. Realizing they’re caught in a dangerous power struggle, and with having just a week until negotiations are over, Shouichi and Emily race against time to uncover the truth and save Azuha.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/06962144bab01a1d50ada404b308a273.avif?t=1775808394\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features RPG-style mechanics where you have to fight enemies, learn new skills, power your characters up, and explore the world. Save your allies from the clutches of evil or avenge them if it's too late.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/709f0c00943a046ff6f72cb48f614fa2.avif?t=1775808394\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/ee25392fe3a2e6a9702aab4a28120289.avif?t=1775808394\" width=739 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/4b89a3ac4444bf5697919ad696f39d7a.avif?t=1775808394\" width=739 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/4a54b9da5f4d09fe7829566b03403e99.avif?t=1775808394\" width=739 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/2d9f387a10217f6a66d2f52975d3eef4.avif?t=1775808394\" width=739 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/a9daae3096e9e147e13fd54331b872d4.avif?t=1775808394\" width=739 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/4dfbf746944436d6e25657c0d1661417.avif?t=1775808394\" width=739 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/163b315185b3acf7a53a87188ce9e03b.avif?t=1775808394\" width=739 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/82dca9cd82688155ea96e2f7f707cc43.avif?t=1775808394\" width=739 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/48fd87783de02d6553afeaf97c9335d5.avif?t=1775808394\" width=739 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/a63a1b4a871103da7ce64f52558bee4e.avif?t=1775808394\" width=739 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/43ca64e8c22b95e22b4783fbb550e87a.avif?t=1775808394\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>RPG</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat enemies to gain experience and level up. Learn new skills and experiment with different skill combinations to face any situation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Resource Management</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Carefully balance limited resources such as time and money to ensure your success through your jouney.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/67adf54c2475c340daf42c5cf8d4b234.avif?t=1775808394\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shouichi, Azuha, and Emily are summoned to another world, but just as they confront the Demon Lord, she escapes to another realm. With no choice, they must follow her to return home. However, they soon discover their abilities are mysteriously sealed, leaving them as ordinary, powerless humans. Azuha, whose powers are desired by King Caldier, volunteers to stay behind in exchange for Shouichi and Emily’s freedom. Feeling something is off, Azuha urges them to gather intel. Realizing they’re caught in a dangerous power struggle, and with having just a week until negotiations are over, Shouichi and Emily race against time to uncover the truth and save Azuha.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/06962144bab01a1d50ada404b308a273.avif?t=1775808394\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features RPG-style mechanics where you have to fight enemies, learn new skills, power your characters up, and explore the world. Save your allies from the clutches of evil or avenge them if it's too late.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/709f0c00943a046ff6f72cb48f614fa2.avif?t=1775808394\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/ee25392fe3a2e6a9702aab4a28120289.avif?t=1775808394\" width=739 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/4b89a3ac4444bf5697919ad696f39d7a.avif?t=1775808394\" width=739 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/4a54b9da5f4d09fe7829566b03403e99.avif?t=1775808394\" width=739 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/2d9f387a10217f6a66d2f52975d3eef4.avif?t=1775808394\" width=739 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/a9daae3096e9e147e13fd54331b872d4.avif?t=1775808394\" width=739 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/4dfbf746944436d6e25657c0d1661417.avif?t=1775808394\" width=739 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/163b315185b3acf7a53a87188ce9e03b.avif?t=1775808394\" width=739 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/82dca9cd82688155ea96e2f7f707cc43.avif?t=1775808394\" width=739 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/48fd87783de02d6553afeaf97c9335d5.avif?t=1775808394\" width=739 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/a63a1b4a871103da7ce64f52558bee4e.avif?t=1775808394\" width=739 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/extras/43ca64e8c22b95e22b4783fbb550e87a.avif?t=1775808394\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>RPG</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat enemies to gain experience and level up. Learn new skills and experiment with different skill combinations to face any situation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Resource Management</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Carefully balance limited resources such as time and money to ensure your success through your jouney.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "short_description": "In this RPG, take on the role of Shouichi, who is summoned to another world alongside Azuha and Emily. With your abilities sealed, you'll need to rely on your wits and teamwork to survive. Will you be able to protect your friends and get them back home safely?", "supported_languages": "English, Japanese, Simplified Chinese, Traditional Chinese", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/83e45cba768510bd678f876c4b79f0e7d9fb2246/header.jpg?t=1775808394", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/09844b32cee94b7c6abce5564e89ad7a7753db3b/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1775808394", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3670820/09844b32cee94b7c6abce5564e89ad7a7753db3b/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1775808394", "website": "https://saikeystudios.com", "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS *:</strong> Windows® 7/8/8.1/10<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Intel Core2 Duo or better<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 4 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> DirectX 9/OpenGL 4.1 capable GPU<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 2 GB available space</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [], "legal_notice": "2026 Saikey Studios", "developers": ["Momimomi Studio"], "publishers": ["Saikey Studios"], "price_overview": {"currency": "USD", "initial": 899, "final": 899, "discount_percent": 0, "initial_formatted": "", "final_formatted": "$8.99"}, "categories": [{"id": 2, "description": "Single-player"}, {"id": 22, "description": "Steam Achievements"}, {"id": 23, "description": "Steam Cloud"}, {"id": 62,